name: Openpen
body:
### Openpen
We are working on some easy way to convert 2D drawing into objects. In this purpose, this module needs to be able to resize and rotate the elements and compare them with the known templates.

## Instalation
There is not some easy installation process yet. Sorry :(
But, you still can just copy our javascript :D
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
